  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<strong>Shaman Spirit Hex</strong><br/><br/><p>A shaman touches a willing creature (including herself ) and grants a bone ward. The warded creature becomes encircled by a group of flying bones that grant it a +2 deflection bonus to AC for a number of rounds equal to the shaman's level. At 8th level, the ward increases to +3 and lasts for 1 minute. At 16th level, the bonus increases to +4 and lasts for 1 hour. Once the bone ward ends, the creature cannot be the target of the hex again for 24 hours.</p>",
